---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping Policy" description="Expert Guru's shipping and delivery policy for online tutoring services.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 via-white to-secondary/10 py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Shipping & Delivery Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          How our services are delivered to you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Expert Guru provides online tutoring services delivered entirely through digital platforms. This page explains how our services are delivered.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Digital Services Only</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Expert Guru is an online tutoring platform. All our services — including 1-on-1 tutoring sessions, study materials, and progress reports — are delivered digitally via our online platform. There are no physical products to ship.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Service Delivery</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Once you enroll and complete payment, here's how our services are delivered:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Account Access:</strong> You will receive login credentials for our tutoring portal within 24 hours of enrollment confirmation.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Session Scheduling:</strong> Your Education Manager will coordinate session schedules within 48 hours of enrollment.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Tutoring Sessions:</strong> All sessions are conducted online via video conferencing with an interactive whiteboard.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Study Materials:</strong> Any supplementary materials, worksheets, or resources are shared digitally through the portal or email.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><strong>Progress Reports:</strong> Monthly progress reports are delivered via email or through the parent portal.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Requirements for Service Delivery</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">To receive our services, you will need:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span>A laptop or desktop computer with a webcam and microphone</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span>A stable internet connection (broadband recommended)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span>A quiet, distraction-free learning environment</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Service Availability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our tutoring sessions are available 7 days a week. Sessions are scheduled based on mutual availability between the tutor and the student, across all time zones. Our platform is accessible 24/7 for portal access, resources, and support.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions About Service Delivery?</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90 mb-4">If you have any questions about how our services are delivered, please contact us:</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">Expert Guru</p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Email: <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="underline">info@expertguru.net</a></p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Website: <a href="https://www.expertguru.net" class="underline">www.expertguru.net</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
